<h1>Sell your old car:</h1>

<%= form_for @product do |f| %>
  <%= f.label :name %>
  <%= f.text_field :name %>
  <%= f.label :How_much_do_you_want? %>
  <%= f.text_field :cost %>
  <%= f.label :country %>
  <%= f.text_field :country %>
  <%= f.submit  %>
<% end %>

<p>Once your car's been set up on our website, any interested buyers will contact us. If the buyer seems legit, we'll contact you within five-to-eight business days.</p>
